This project is for API By Symfony5
First : install The symfony CLI
Second create the project : composer create-project symfony/skeleton my_project_name
symfony check:req

run in the background : symfony serve -d
Packages :
   - composer require annotations
   - composer require symfony/maker-bundle --dev
   - composer require sec-checker

Some Notes:
- Check IdMembre dans l'equipe qui peut travailler sur le projet

- Must create EventSubscriber so when Member register, send him email (sendEmail inside EventSubscriber) 
   Take notes from UserRegisterSubscriber of symfony-api-platform

- Must add Validator and Validation constraints using regular 
  expressions in entities like Member for passwords checks etc..., 
   @UniqueEntity("email", groups={"post"})
  Take notes from User entity of symfony-api-platform

- use this bundle for Token : composer require lexik/jwt-authentication-bundle
- Must make the private key and public
   openssl genrsa -out config/jwt/private.pem -aes256 512
   openssl rsa -pubout -in config/jwt/private.pem -out config/jwt/public.pem
- Remake The login following security part of symfony-api-platform

Maker Use List Command:
- php bin/console list make
- php bin/console make:auth

List of routes:
- php bin/console debug:router

Migrations:
0 - php bin/console doctrine:database:create
1 - php bin/console make:migration
2 - php bin/console doctrine:migrations:migrate